
            [*] Welcome to the reality of Primal Darkness! [*]

The following information should be of use to new players:
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
            Your first act should be to type <faq> and <help rules>.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
            Direct questions to Whit, Daos, or Stormbringer
            or use the newbie line to ask players on a question.
            You can do that by typing "newbie <your question>" 
            For example "newbie I'm lost how do I play?" type that
            without quotes.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
            For wielding of weapons, type <help wield>.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
            If you have a colour terminal, type <ansi on> to
            see the mud in colour.

